{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, in contrast to CNN-DM, both the textual content and summaries within XSum are more concise, while simultaneously showcasing a more extensive lexicon.",
    "• AGNEWS (Zhang et al, 2015).",
    "The AGNEWS dataset encompasses 497K news articles sourced from a diverse array of over 2K news outlets.",
    "It functions as an evaluative benchmark for gauging the efficacy of models in the realm of news article topic classification.",
    "The news topics are broadly classified into four categories: world, sports, business, and science & technology."
  ]
}